{"tid":939444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國所捉人質　不是前加拿大外交官　是現任外交官　休假做hk ngo","createTime":"2018-12-13T06:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T02:01:27.000Z","uid":47714,"like":203,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c6e2c2ab41590e682f5d466d859a897320ca6a","tid":939444,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T06:44:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2018/12/12/canada-will-follow-rule-of-law-in-huawei-extradition-case-justin-trudeau-says.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestar.com%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2Fcanada-will-follow-rule-of-law-in-huawei-extradition-case-justin-trudeau-says.html&d=KnvXPE3nScOl%2BNY7DWqCyp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=b0b10360\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2018/12/12/canada-will-follow-rule-of-law-in-huawei-extradition-case-justin-trudeau-says.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0bxkvu5sgUQ/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F0bxkvu5sgUQ%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=1c0130da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA second Canadian citizen appears to be in trouble in China. A Canadian man flagged his concern about being questioned by Chinese authorities to Canadian officials, but Foreign Affairs Minister Chrystia Freeland says Canada has now lost contact with that Canadian man.....<br />\n<br />\nKovrig was on special leave to work with a non-governmental organization in Hong Kong, does not have diplomatic status, yet is considered to still be an employee of the department. &ldquo;It adds another layer to the concern,&rdquo; admitted Freeland. She said the government has a special duty of care to its own employees, but it is &ldquo;agonizing&rdquo; when any Canadian is detained outside Canada.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCPForum/posts/2633074423377375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCPForum%2Fposts%2F2633074423377375&d=KnvXPE3nScOl%2BNY7DWqCyp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f38adc11\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCPForum/posts/2633074423377375</a><br />\n<br />\nKovrig 原來仍然是加拿大外交官。只是take leave 去做NGO 嘢！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2324599847776093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2324599847776093&d=KnvXPE3nScOl%2BNY7DWqCyp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=108ade3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2324599847776093</a><br />\n<br />\n香港NGO <img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t2c/1/16/1f631.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft2c%2F1%2F16%2F1f631.png&h=44ff6c9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32bd6dc30f693aca671749c0b673bb9a221bc8bd","tid":939444,"uid":108467,"like":156,"dislike":0,"score":156,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T06:45:41.000Z","msg":"中國人政府做嘢唔用腦諗下<br />\n咁又係，習總得小學教育程度😂"},{"pid":"4fe50154b4ee32c11ec37533584103f257b437c3","tid":939444,"uid":221801,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T06:47:23.000Z","msg":"做咩啫 咁依加咪捉過第二個囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae959c0cdbc4469b2ae270928dcf4c54b859b9cf","tid":939444,"uid":28759,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T06:53:09.000Z","msg":"喺香港捉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630d1773c8424f5ce6a138f38079f259f1af7292","tid":939444,"uid":39200,"like":100,"dislike":2,"score":98,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T06:53:50.000Z","msg":"咩呀, 捉你咪捉你, 你話佢捉錯就即刻捉多一個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過埋今個新年中國大陸就唔架在, 改國號雜國, 八國聯軍好快跪低圍含雜帝架啦"},{"pid":"9f4fbab84a35943481ccd357e32c5135612d43f5","tid":939444,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s